snippet.title: Demonsions: Industry - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Demonsions: Industry is an open-world, procedurally generated factory builder game inspired by Minecraft and Satisfactory. Planned Early Access Release Date: 4/22/21. I am the Lead/Sole Developer.

Vyrulent.com
Find me on twitter @DemonsionsDev

Get Early Access on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1592020/Demonsions_Industry/

Demo available at Vyrulent.com
